First Department,

October, 1981

(October 22, 1981)* In the Matter of Gene Loy Chu, a Disbarred Attorney.

Not published with other decisions of October 22, 1981, 84 AD2d 518 [Rep.

Petition seeking to vacate or modify order of disbarment denied. Concur — Murphy, P. J., Kupferman, Sandler, Markewich and Silverman, JJ.
